### Gardens API

### List all gardens
GET http://localhost:8080/gardens
Accept: application/json

### Get garden by ID
GET http://localhost:8080/gardens/1
Accept: application/json

### Create garden
POST http://localhost:8080/gardens
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "address": "Schulgasse 12, 4020 Linz"
}

### Update garden
PUT http://localhost:8080/gardens/1
Content-Type: application/json

{
  "address": "Neue Adresse 99"
}

### Delete garden
DELETE http://localhost:8080/gardens/1
